WEBVTT

00:01.169 --> 00:03.037
- IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE
SYSTEM,

00:03.071 --> 00:06.240
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:06.274 --> 00:09.077
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:09.110 --> 00:10.678
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:10.711 --> 00:12.346
ARE MEMBERS
OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:12.380 --> 00:14.215
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:14.248 --> 00:16.550
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:18.819 --> 00:22.690
[water running]

00:22.723 --> 00:24.325
- AH.
- AH!

00:24.358 --> 00:26.294
UH!
- OW! OW!

00:26.327 --> 00:27.161
UGH!

00:27.195 --> 00:29.797
COME ON, YOU CAN'T
GET AWAY FROM ME.

00:29.830 --> 00:32.466
- OH, NO!
OH.

00:32.500 --> 00:33.801
- YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE
DONE THAT.

00:33.834 --> 00:37.105
[panting]

00:37.138 --> 00:38.339
AH.
- UGH.

00:38.372 --> 00:40.808
HA! YOU'RE DEAD.

00:40.841 --> 00:45.179
- DISARM, EVADE,
AND ESCAPE, BELLE.

00:45.213 --> 00:47.815
YOU'RE TRAINING
TO SURVIVE, NOT TO KILL.

00:51.752 --> 00:53.654
MM.

00:53.687 --> 00:58.259
- [loud scream]

00:58.292 --> 01:00.528
- OH, MY GOD, CATHERINE.

01:00.561 --> 01:04.332
- HE--HE WENT OUT
THE WINDOW.

01:04.365 --> 01:06.434
- I DON'T SEE ANYBODY.
- OLIVER, CALL THE POLICE

01:06.467 --> 01:07.868
AND TELL THEM TO MEET US
AT THE HOSPITAL.

01:07.901 --> 01:09.403
- NO HOSPITAL!

01:09.437 --> 01:11.505
BELLE, I CAN'T.

01:11.539 --> 01:13.707
[sobbing]

01:13.741 --> 01:15.443
- CAT, YOU NEED A DOCTOR.

01:15.476 --> 01:17.178
YOU WERE RAPED.

01:18.546 --> 01:20.114
- I DON'T WANNA BE HERE.

01:20.148 --> 01:21.749
- MS. HARRISON...

01:21.782 --> 01:24.785
I'M DETECTIVE STABLER,
MY PARTNER, DETECTIVE TUTUOLA.

01:24.818 --> 01:27.688
YOU FEEL UP TO TALKING?
- IT'S ABOUT TIME.

01:27.721 --> 01:29.557
- I'M SORRY, YOU ARE?
- ISABELLE.

01:29.590 --> 01:30.891
SHE'S MY BEST FRIEND.

01:30.924 --> 01:33.561
- CAN YOU TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED?

01:33.594 --> 01:36.330
- THERE'S NOT MUCH TO TELL.

01:36.364 --> 01:39.733
I WAS EXHAUSTED
AND WENT TO BED EARLY.

01:39.767 --> 01:42.270
- CAT TEACHES NINTH GRADE
AT JEFFERSON HIGH.

01:42.303 --> 01:46.407
- WHEN I WOKE UP,
HE WAS ALREADY ON TOP OF ME.

01:46.440 --> 01:48.576
HIS HAND OVER MY MOUTH.

01:48.609 --> 01:50.278
- HOW'D HE GET IN?
- THROUGH THE WINDOW.

01:50.311 --> 01:52.513
THERE'S A FIRE ESCAPE.
- I GUESS I DIDN'T LOCK IT.

01:52.546 --> 01:54.615
HOW COULD I BE SO STUPID?

01:54.648 --> 01:56.484
- CAT, DON'T YOU DARE
BLAME YOURSELF.

01:56.517 --> 01:57.618
- DID HE SAY ANYTHING?

01:57.651 --> 02:00.354
- NO. HE...

02:00.388 --> 02:02.590
RIPPED MY NIGHTGOWN
AND MY UNDERWEAR,

02:02.623 --> 02:05.626
PANTING IN MY EAR,
PAWING AT ME.

02:05.659 --> 02:07.895
- YOU SEE HIS FACE?
HIS BODY TYPE?

02:07.928 --> 02:10.564
HIS RACE?
- IT WAS TOO DARK.

02:10.598 --> 02:12.700
- IT WAS PROBABLY ONE
OF THOSE HOODLUMS FROM SCHOOL.

02:12.733 --> 02:15.236
- [sighs]
MY STUDENTS WOULDN'T ATTACK ME.

02:15.269 --> 02:16.504
THEY'RE GOOD KIDS.

02:16.537 --> 02:17.771
- GOOD AT ROBBING,
RAPING, AND RAISING HELL.

02:17.805 --> 02:19.473
- DON'T ACCUSE THEM,
THEY GET ENOUGH OF THAT

02:19.507 --> 02:20.874
FROM EVERYONE ELSE.
- WITH GOOD REASON.

02:20.908 --> 02:22.643
THEY'RE A BUNCH OF--
- ISABELLE,

02:22.676 --> 02:25.679
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU OUTSIDE,
I'LL TAKE YOUR STATEMENT.

02:35.456 --> 02:36.690
- YOU KNOW
WHO ATTACKED YOU.

02:38.426 --> 02:40.428
- HE LIVES IN
THE APARTMENT DOWNSTAIRS.

02:40.461 --> 02:42.296
- WHO IS IT?

02:42.330 --> 02:45.333
- KEVIN.

02:47.435 --> 02:49.503
ISABELLE'S OLDER BROTHER.

02:49.537 --> 02:51.672
[crying]

02:54.742 --> 02:57.711
[dramatic music]

02:57.745 --> 03:03.817
*

03:41.655 --> 03:42.856
- ISABELLE, DID YOU SEE
OR HEAR ANYTHING

03:42.890 --> 03:45.859
DURING CATHERINE'S ATTACK?
- I WISH I HAD.

03:45.893 --> 03:49.897
AND MY BOYFRIEND, OLIVER,
IS TEACHING ME KRAV MAGA.

03:49.930 --> 03:51.732
I TRIED TO GET CAT
TO TAKE A CLASS,

03:51.765 --> 03:54.001
BUT SHE WAS ALWAYS TOO BUSY
TRYING TO SAVE THOSE HOOD RATS.

03:54.034 --> 03:56.003
- DID SHE EVER MENTION
ANY OF HER KIDS

03:56.036 --> 03:56.937
THREATENING HER?
- YES.

03:56.970 --> 03:58.539
THAT SCHOOL'S A ZOO.

03:58.572 --> 03:59.873
MOST OF THEM
ALREADY HAVE RECORDS.

03:59.907 --> 04:01.709
[phone rings]
GO THERE, YOU'LL SEE.

04:01.742 --> 04:03.544
- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
IT WAS ISABELLE'S BROTHER

04:03.577 --> 04:04.945
WHO ATTACKED YOU?

04:04.978 --> 04:08.749
- KEVIN'S ALWAYS ON
THE FIRE ESCAPE, HANGING OUT.

04:08.782 --> 04:12.286
I'VE CAUGHT HIM WATCHING ME
THROUGH THE WINDOW.

04:12.320 --> 04:13.253
- WAS HE OUT THERE
LAST NIGHT?

04:13.287 --> 04:17.758
- AROUND 7:30,
WHILE I WAS GRADING PAPERS.

04:17.791 --> 04:20.394
- AND YOU...

04:20.428 --> 04:21.829
OBVIOUSLY
DIDN'T TELL ISABELLE.

04:21.862 --> 04:24.332
- HOW COULD I?

04:24.365 --> 04:26.567
HE'S HER BROTHER.

04:26.600 --> 04:28.436
- IS YOUR FAMILY CLOSE
TO CATHERINE?

04:28.469 --> 04:30.037
- MY BROTHER KNOWS CAT.

04:30.070 --> 04:32.039
BUT HE BARELY TALKS TO HER.

04:32.072 --> 04:33.874
ANYONE REALLY.
KEVIN LIVES IN HIS OWN HEAD.

04:33.907 --> 04:36.076
- MENTALLY ILL?
- BIPOLAR.

04:36.109 --> 04:38.979
AGORAPHOBIC, TOO.

04:39.012 --> 04:41.014
WHY THE HELL ARE YOU
ASKING ME ABOUT KEVIN?

04:41.048 --> 04:43.083
HE DIDN'T ATTACK CAT.
- IT CROSSED YOUR MIND.

04:43.116 --> 04:44.585
THAT'S WHY YOU ACCUSED
HER STUDENTS.

04:44.618 --> 04:45.886
[door opening]

04:45.919 --> 04:47.688
- MR. HARRISON.
- WHERE IS SHE?

04:47.721 --> 04:50.724
- IN THERE.

04:52.360 --> 04:54.395
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
CATHERINE?

04:54.428 --> 04:56.464
- A LITTLE SHAKY,
BUT I'LL BE FINE.

04:56.497 --> 04:58.065
- OH, GOD.

04:58.098 --> 05:00.067
- I'M DETECTIVE STABLER.

05:00.100 --> 05:01.735
- OH.

05:01.769 --> 05:03.737
THANK YOU FOR CALLING,
DETECTIVE.

05:03.771 --> 05:06.073
I HAD NO IDEA
MY GRANDDAUGHTER

05:06.106 --> 05:07.641
WAS HURT
AND ALL ALONE.

05:07.675 --> 05:09.042
- I WASN'T ALONE.

05:09.076 --> 05:10.644
ISABELLE TOOK CARE OF ME.

05:10.678 --> 05:12.613
- YOU ARE COMING HOME
WITH ME.

05:12.646 --> 05:14.748
- NO, I'LL BE FINE
IN MY APARTMENT.

05:14.782 --> 05:15.949
- CATHERINE,
YOU REALLY SHOULD

05:15.983 --> 05:17.918
STAY SOMEWHERE ELSE
UNTIL WE MAKE AN ARREST.

05:17.951 --> 05:20.654
- YOU SEE?
YOU'LL BE SAFER WITH ME.

05:20.688 --> 05:24.492
- BELLE'S GONNA HATE ME NOW.

05:24.525 --> 05:26.927
- SHE'S NOT YOUR FRIEND.

05:26.960 --> 05:29.096
I WILL TAKE CARE OF YOU.
- [crying]

05:29.129 --> 05:30.998
- AW.

05:31.031 --> 05:32.966
- ISABELLE'S BROTHER,
KEVIN WRIGHT,

05:33.000 --> 05:34.968
PLED GUILTY
TO UNLAWFUL SURVEILLANCE,

05:35.002 --> 05:37.104
SECOND DEGREE,
IN MARCH 2008.

05:37.137 --> 05:41.141
HE WAS REGISTERED AS
A LEVEL TWO SEX OFFENDER.

05:41.174 --> 05:43.944
HE TOOK PHOTOS OF A WOMAN
UNDRESSING IN HER BEDROOM

05:43.977 --> 05:44.945
FROM THE ROOF
OF HIS BUILDING.

05:44.978 --> 05:47.147
THEN HE TRIED TO TELL
THE COPS HE WAS TAKING

05:47.180 --> 05:49.517
STILLS FOR HIS JOB
AT AN ENGINEERING FIRM.

05:49.550 --> 05:51.652
- WE GOT SEVERAL ARRESTS FOR
TRESPASSING ON THE SAME BLOCK.

05:51.685 --> 05:52.953
[phone ringing]
- HEY, GUYS...

05:52.986 --> 05:54.121
LIFTED TWO DOZEN PRINTS

05:54.154 --> 05:57.024
BELONGING TO KEVIN WRIGHT
FROM THE FIRE ESCAPE OUTSIDE

05:57.057 --> 05:58.859
THE VICTIM'S WINDOW.
- ANY PRINTS INSIDE?

05:58.892 --> 06:01.529
- NOPE. BUT THE LAB'S
STILL PROCESSING THE BEDDING.

06:01.562 --> 06:03.731
PRELIMINARY REPORT
SHOWS NO FLUIDS.

06:03.764 --> 06:05.966
- SO WE GOT NOTHING PUTTING HIM
IN CATHERINE'S BEDROOM.

06:05.999 --> 06:09.136
- WELL, WE DID RECOVER A PARTIAL
SHOE IMPRESSION BY THE BED.

06:09.169 --> 06:11.038
LOOKS LIKE
A MEN'S SIZE 11.

06:11.071 --> 06:13.106
- WELL, YOU GOT ENOUGH
DETAIL FOR A COMPARISON?

06:13.140 --> 06:14.475
- WHEN WE KNOW,
YOU'LL KNOW.

06:14.508 --> 06:15.843
- HUH.

06:15.876 --> 06:17.945
WELL, IF KEVIN WRIGHT
WEARS A SIZE 11, WE GOT HIM.

06:17.978 --> 06:19.913
- DON'T BOTHER
TRYING HIM AT HIS OFFICE.

06:19.947 --> 06:23.517
HE GOT FIRED TWO DAYS AGO
FOR ACTING CRAZY.

06:23.551 --> 06:25.018
- IT'S A GOOD THING
WE KNOW WHERE HE LIVES.

06:27.220 --> 06:28.956
- KEVIN SAID HE
DIDN'T EVEN TOUCH YOU.

06:28.989 --> 06:30.157
HE'S NEVER EVEN BEEN
TO YOUR ROOM.

06:30.190 --> 06:32.025
- BELLE, I'M SORRY,
BUT IT WAS HIM.

06:32.059 --> 06:33.193
- YOU SAID YOU DIDN'T
SEE HIS FACE.

06:33.226 --> 06:34.862
- HEY, HEY, HEY!
WHAT'S GOING ON?

06:34.895 --> 06:37.965
- SHE'S ACCUSING MY BROTHER.
- I'M NOT MAKING IT UP.

06:37.998 --> 06:39.500
- CATHERINE,
YOU AND YOUR GRANDFATHER,

06:39.533 --> 06:40.934
IT'S TIME TO LEAVE.
- COME ON, CATHERINE.

06:40.968 --> 06:42.703
YOU DON'T BELONG HERE.
- AND NEITHER DO YOU.

06:42.736 --> 06:44.572
THEY'RE TRESPASSING.
ARREST THEM.

06:44.605 --> 06:45.839
- ENOUGH.
ENOUGH.

06:45.873 --> 06:47.040
SIR, IT'S TIME TO LEAVE.

06:47.074 --> 06:49.477
- I ALWAYS SAID
THIS WAS A BAD NEIGHBORHOOD.

06:49.510 --> 06:51.912
- WHERE'S YOUR BROTHER?

06:51.945 --> 06:52.913
- I DON'T KNOW.

06:52.946 --> 06:54.715
BUT HE'S DONE NOTHING
WRONG.

06:54.748 --> 06:56.617
- JUST ENOUGH
TO GET HIMSELF FIRED.

06:56.650 --> 06:58.752
- HE'S A BRILLIANT ENGINEER,
YOU KNOW.

06:58.786 --> 07:01.622
HE BUILDS BRIDGES.

07:01.655 --> 07:03.090
HE MUST'VE STOPPED
TAKING HIS MEDS.

07:03.123 --> 07:04.224
- HE DO THAT A LOT?

07:04.257 --> 07:06.627
- EVERY COUPLE OF YEARS,
HE THINKS HE DOESN'T NEED THEM.

07:06.660 --> 07:09.530
- AND WHEN HE DOESN'T
TAKE THEM?

07:09.563 --> 07:11.499
- HE GETS OUT OF CONTROL.
- WELL, THAT'S EXACTLY

07:11.532 --> 07:15.202
WHY YOU SHOULD
HELP US FIND HIM.

07:15.235 --> 07:18.972
- I HAVE HIS KEYS
IN MY APARTMENT.

07:19.006 --> 07:20.841
YOU'VE GOT THIS
ALL WRONG.

07:20.874 --> 07:21.975
KEVIN'S NEVER BEEN VIOLENT.

07:22.009 --> 07:23.644
- YOU HEARD CATHERINE SCREAM.

07:23.677 --> 07:24.712
SOMEBODY ATTACKED HER,

07:24.745 --> 07:26.580
AND YOU ACT LIKE
YOU DON'T EVEN CARE.

07:26.614 --> 07:28.516
- THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN SAY
TO MAKE ME BELIEVE

07:28.549 --> 07:30.083
MY BROTHER'S GUILTY.

07:30.117 --> 07:32.085
- WELL, I GUESS
IF YOUR BEST FRIEND

07:32.119 --> 07:33.587
CAN'T CONVINCE YOU,
NO ONE CAN.

07:33.621 --> 07:35.823
LOOK, ISABELLE, A LOT OF--
- CAUGHT HIM, EL,

07:35.856 --> 07:37.124
HE'S GOING UP
THE FIRE ESCAPE.

07:37.157 --> 07:38.191
- MEET YOU UP THERE!

07:38.225 --> 07:39.693
- PLEASE DON'T HURT HIM.

07:44.632 --> 07:45.966
- KEVIN!

07:45.999 --> 07:47.568
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.
YOU OKAY?

07:47.601 --> 07:48.902
- I DON'T FEEL LIKE IT.
GO AWAY.

07:48.936 --> 07:51.038
- I CAN'T DO THAT.
YOU NEED TO COME INSIDE.

07:51.071 --> 07:52.806
- I CAN'T BREATHE IN THERE.

07:52.840 --> 07:55.709
- THAT'S 'CAUSE YOU
HAVEN'T BEEN TAKING YOUR MEDS.

07:55.743 --> 07:57.845
- AND THE WORLD
IS GLORIOUS.

07:57.878 --> 07:58.979
- WHOA, WHOA!
STOP!

07:59.012 --> 08:01.749
- LOOK AROUND.
LOOK.

08:01.782 --> 08:07.054
NO ONE APPRECIATES...
THE DETAIL

08:07.087 --> 08:09.122
AND THE CRAFTSMANSHIP...

08:09.156 --> 08:13.827
THAT GOES
INTO A STRUCTURE.

08:13.861 --> 08:16.129
ISN'T THAT GRAND?

08:16.163 --> 08:20.200
- I'M SORRY I DON'T
APPRECIATE IT THE WAY YOU DO.

08:20.233 --> 08:22.803
- I LIVE IN...

08:22.836 --> 08:25.272
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL CITY

08:25.305 --> 08:29.076
IN THE WORLD.

08:29.109 --> 08:31.078
AND I HATE IT.

08:31.111 --> 08:33.681
- COME ON, KEVIN.
- GET OFF MY ROOF!

08:33.714 --> 08:34.848
- COME ON, MAN.
LISTEN,

08:34.882 --> 08:36.984
WHAT YOU'RE FEELING
ISN'T REAL.

08:37.017 --> 08:39.987
- [laughing]

08:40.020 --> 08:42.222
I HAVE CLEANSED MYSELF.

08:42.255 --> 08:44.692
AND NOW...

08:44.725 --> 08:46.259
I'M GONNA FLY.

08:52.733 --> 08:54.234
- [grunts]

08:54.267 --> 08:56.804
- A ONE-WAY
TRIP TO BELLEVUE.

08:56.837 --> 08:58.939
- BIG FEET THERE.
WHAT ARE YOU, SIZE 11?

08:58.972 --> 09:01.274
- KEVIN!
WHAT WERE YOU TRYING TO DO?

09:01.308 --> 09:04.311
- I HAD TO GET SOME AIR,
BELLES.

09:06.013 --> 09:09.549
I CAN'T BREATHE.

09:18.391 --> 09:19.827
- SORRY, DETECTIVES,

09:19.860 --> 09:21.028
YOU CAN'T TALK TO
MY PATIENT RIGHT NOW.

09:21.061 --> 09:22.596
- DR. WUNSTELL,
HE IS A RAPE SUSPECT.

09:22.630 --> 09:24.598
- AND AT THE MOMENT,
UNRESPONSIVE.

09:24.632 --> 09:25.999
- WHAT DID YOU
PUMP HIM FULL OF?

09:26.033 --> 09:28.068
- HALOPERIDOL
AND DIAZEPAM.

09:28.101 --> 09:30.037
- WELL, ANYTHING
HE SAYS UNDER THE INFLUENCE

09:30.070 --> 09:31.371
IS INADMISSIBLE.
- WOULD YOU PREFER

09:31.404 --> 09:33.140
KEVIN TRY
TO KILL HIMSELF AGAIN?

09:33.173 --> 09:35.008
- HOW LONG TILL
IT'S OUT OF HIS SYSTEM?

09:35.042 --> 09:37.978
- HE'LL STAY SEDATED UNTIL
I CAN EVALUATE HIS MENTAL STATE.

09:38.011 --> 09:40.714
HE'S SUICIDAL, ANXIOUS,
AND DEPRESSED.

09:40.748 --> 09:42.683
I'D LIKE TO KNOW WHY.

09:42.716 --> 09:46.219
- IT'S CALLED 25 TO LIFE.

09:46.253 --> 09:50.223
- NOT THIS GUY'S
FIRST VISIT TO CRAZY TOWN.

09:50.257 --> 09:52.860
- WELL, IT'S A LIFETIME
OF MEDICAL RECORDS.

09:52.893 --> 09:55.228
DIAGNOSED
CLINICALLY DEPRESSED AT 17,

09:55.262 --> 09:56.664
BIPOLAR AT 20.

09:56.697 --> 09:58.766
- THEY'RE ALL JUST AMMO
FOR HIS LAWYER.

09:58.799 --> 09:59.733
- [softly groans]

09:59.767 --> 10:02.402
- HARDWICKE'S IN MIAMI
AT A BAR CONFERENCE.

10:02.435 --> 10:04.672
ANYONE KNOW
WHO'S OUR TEMPORARY A.D.A.?

10:04.705 --> 10:07.240
- HOW ABOUT ONE
BACK FROM THE DEAD?

10:07.274 --> 10:09.409
- CASEY NOVAK.

10:09.442 --> 10:11.144
- ALIVE AND FAIRLY WELL.

10:11.178 --> 10:13.246
- GOOD TO SEE YOU
AGAIN, CASEY.

10:13.280 --> 10:14.715
- EXCEPT I THOUGHT YOU
WERE DISBARRED.

10:14.748 --> 10:15.883
- OH, CENSURED.

10:15.916 --> 10:17.417
LOST MY LICENSE
FOR THREE YEARS,

10:17.450 --> 10:19.853
BUT THE D.A.'S OFFICE
HIRED ME BACK.

10:19.887 --> 10:21.354
BUT I'M STILL ON PROBATION.

10:21.388 --> 10:22.422
SO WHAT HAVE WE GOT?

10:22.455 --> 10:25.158
- A RAPE IN WASHINGTON HEIGHTS
THREE NIGHTS AGO.

10:25.192 --> 10:27.895
- THE VICTIM SAYS IT
WAS HER DOWNSTAIRS NEIGHBOR.

10:27.928 --> 10:30.163
- SO SHE SAW HIS FACE.
- NO.

10:30.197 --> 10:31.965
- SHE RECOGNIZED HIS VOICE?

10:31.999 --> 10:33.133
- PERP DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING.

10:33.166 --> 10:35.703
BUT...SHE KNOWS THE GUY.

10:35.736 --> 10:37.871
- SO ALL WE HAVE IS
A SHAKY I.D. AND NO EVIDENCE.

10:37.905 --> 10:39.139
WELCOME HOME.

10:39.172 --> 10:40.708
- YEAH, WELL,
WE GOT FINGERPRINTS

10:40.741 --> 10:42.976
ON THE FIRE ESCAPE
LEADING INTO HER BEDROOM.

10:43.010 --> 10:44.311
- AND WE ALSO HAVE
A PARTIAL SHOE PRINT

10:44.344 --> 10:46.346
MATCHING
HIS SIZE 11 FEET.

10:46.379 --> 10:48.415
- SO WHAT DO WE KNOW
ABOUT OUR SUSPECT?

10:48.448 --> 10:49.683
- KEVIN WRIGHT.

10:49.717 --> 10:51.118
HE WAS
INVOLUNTARILY COMMITTED

10:51.151 --> 10:53.286
ABOUT THREE YEARS AGO
BY THE COURT.

10:53.320 --> 10:54.755
HE DID TWO MONTHS
IN CREEDMOOR

10:54.788 --> 10:56.189
FOR SLICING
HIS OWN WRISTS.

10:56.223 --> 10:58.225
- AND A FEW DAYS AGO,
HE TRIED TO LEAP OFF

10:58.258 --> 11:00.193
A FIFTH STORY WALK-UP.

11:00.227 --> 11:02.796
THIS GUY JUST CANNOT
GET IT TOGETHER.

11:02.830 --> 11:04.231
- OR HE DOESN'T REALLY
WANNA DIE.

11:04.264 --> 11:07.100
- COURT-ORDERED THERAPY
AND HEAVY MEDICATION.

11:07.134 --> 11:09.837
THE GUY'S GOT
NIGHT TERRORS, MOOD SWINGS,

11:09.870 --> 11:11.338
AND CLINICAL DEPRESSION.

11:11.371 --> 11:13.941
- HE WAS
SEXUALLY ASSAULTED.

11:13.974 --> 11:17.077
CREEDMOOR PSYCHIATRISTS
DIAGNOSED KEVIN

11:17.110 --> 11:18.478
WITH RAPE TRAUMA SYNDROME.

11:18.511 --> 11:20.781
- SO OUR PERP WAS ONCE
A VICTIM HIMSELF.

11:22.249 --> 11:23.884
- YEAH, EXCEPT HIS NAME

11:23.917 --> 11:25.452
IS NOT IN THE DATABASE
FOR THE ASSAULT.

11:25.485 --> 11:26.954
- BUT IT DOESN'T MEAN
IT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

11:26.987 --> 11:29.489
A LOT OF VICTIMS
DON'T REPORT, ESPECIALLY MEN.

11:29.522 --> 11:31.358
- YOU KNOW, IF IT DID HAPPEN,
YOU GOT MOTIVE.

11:31.391 --> 11:32.793
HOW MANY VICTIMS
BECOME PREDATORS?

11:32.826 --> 11:34.261
- PRISONS
ARE FULL OF THEM.

11:34.294 --> 11:37.297
THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM
FOR ONE MORE.

11:39.099 --> 11:41.434
- LOOK, KEVIN...

11:41.468 --> 11:43.737
WE KNOW THERE'S BEEN
A LOT OF TRAUMA IN YOUR LIFE.

11:43.771 --> 11:45.873
ALL RIGHT?
WE KNOW YOU WERE ABUSED.

11:45.906 --> 11:49.810
- LOOK,
I DIDN'T HURT ANYBODY

11:49.843 --> 11:52.846
BECAUSE I HAD
A CRAPPY CHILDHOOD.

11:54.214 --> 11:56.817
EVERYONE
HAS A CRAZY UNCLE.

11:56.850 --> 11:58.418
I WAS LEFT ALONE WITH MINE.
BIG DEAL.

11:58.451 --> 11:59.519
- WELL, IT IS A BIG DEAL

11:59.552 --> 12:01.822
WHEN YOU RAPE SOMEBODY
IN YOUR APARTMENT BUILDING.

12:01.855 --> 12:05.225
- YOU KNOW, MOST
SEX OFFENDERS WERE MOLESTED.

12:05.258 --> 12:08.428
AND THERE'S A PAIN THAT
FESTERS AND TURNS INTO RAGE,

12:08.461 --> 12:10.230
AND THEN BEFORE YOU KNOW IT,
YOU'RE PICKING OUT A VICTIM

12:10.263 --> 12:12.833
THAT YOU THINK
HAD IT COMING TO THEM.

12:12.866 --> 12:14.401
RIGHT, NOW IS THAT
WHAT HAPPENED?

12:14.434 --> 12:16.870
- NO.
I DON'T EVEN KNOW CATHERINE.

12:16.904 --> 12:18.171
- SHE'S YOUR SISTER'S
BEST FRIEND,

12:18.205 --> 12:19.506
SHE LIVES RIGHT ABOVE YOU.

12:19.539 --> 12:21.308
TRY AGAIN.

12:21.341 --> 12:23.543
- I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE SHE'S AFRAID OF ME.

12:23.576 --> 12:25.813
- AND THAT MAKES YOU MAD.
- I'M TELLING YOU,

12:25.846 --> 12:26.947
I COULDN'T CARE LESS
ABOUT THAT GIRL.

12:26.980 --> 12:28.315
- SO WHAT
WERE YOUR FINGERPRINTS

12:28.348 --> 12:30.383
DOING ON THE FIRE ESCAPE
OUTSIDE HER BEDROOM?

12:30.417 --> 12:31.785
- 'CAUSE I GO UP
TO THE ROOF A LOT.

12:31.819 --> 12:33.286
- WHEN YOU'RE
NOT PEEKING IN WINDOWS.

12:33.320 --> 12:35.823
- NO, I GO UP THERE
TO LOOK AT BRIDGES.

12:35.856 --> 12:37.257
THEY'RE MY PASSION.

12:37.290 --> 12:39.326
I CAN SEE THEM
FROM UP ON THE ROOFTOP.

12:39.359 --> 12:41.028
- WELL, KEVIN, WE THINK YOU
WERE DOING A LITTLE MORE

12:41.061 --> 12:42.495
THAN JUST LOOKING AT BRIDGES.

12:42.529 --> 12:44.832
- [sighs]

12:44.865 --> 12:47.167
I KNOW WHAT CATHERINE
SAID ABOUT ME.

12:47.200 --> 12:49.169
BUT I NEVER
WENT INTO HER ROOM.

12:49.202 --> 12:50.871
- SO WHAT WAS YOUR
FOOTPRINT DOING IN HER ROOM?

12:50.904 --> 12:52.439
- IT WASN'T MINE!

12:52.472 --> 12:55.542
LOOK, I SWEAR, I HAVEN'T
SET FOOT IN THAT APARTMENT

12:55.575 --> 12:58.778
SINCE SHE MOVED IN
WITH MY SISTER.

13:01.181 --> 13:02.883
- HE WASN'T
LYING ABOUT BRIDGES.

13:02.916 --> 13:05.185
- I PULLED THESE PICS
OUT OF HIS DIGITAL CAMERA.

13:05.218 --> 13:06.519
- SO BRIDGE-GAZING
IS A HOBBY, HUH?

13:06.553 --> 13:10.190
- HE'S GOT THE GW, HIGH BRIDGE,
WARDS ISLAND BRIDGE.

13:10.223 --> 13:13.060
HIS FIXATION IS WEIRD,
BUT IT'S NOT CRIMINAL.

13:13.093 --> 13:16.063
- UNTIL HE AIMED HIS LENS
AT A LADY UNDRESSING.

13:16.096 --> 13:17.464
GOT POPPED
AS A SEX OFFENDER.

13:17.497 --> 13:18.899
- THAT'S IT?
IT LOOKS LIKE

13:18.932 --> 13:20.901
SHE JUST HAPPENED
TO BE IN THE PICTURE.

13:20.934 --> 13:21.869
- THESE PHOTOS CERTAINLY
PUT THAT ONE

13:21.902 --> 13:23.236
IN A DIFFERENT CONTEXT.
- YEAH.

13:23.270 --> 13:25.839
KEVIN WRIGHT GOT SHAFTED,
HE NEEDED A BETTER LAWYER.

13:25.873 --> 13:28.175
- OR A LESS-AMBITIOUS
PROSECUTOR.

13:28.208 --> 13:30.277
'CAUSE I DO KNOW ONE
WHEN I SEE ONE.

13:30.310 --> 13:32.245
I ALSO KNOW A CASE
WHEN IT FALLS APART.

13:32.279 --> 13:33.513
- WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED
TO MEAN?

13:33.546 --> 13:35.849
- CATHERINE'S RAPE KIT
GAVE US DIDDLY--

13:35.883 --> 13:37.851
NO FOREIGN HAIRS,
TRACE, OR FLUIDS.

13:37.885 --> 13:40.220
AND C.S.U.
SAYS THE TRACE EVIDENCE

13:40.253 --> 13:41.188
ON THE PARTIAL SHOE PRINT

13:41.221 --> 13:43.590
COMES FROM A TYPE OF
CAFETERIA CLEANING AGENT

13:43.623 --> 13:45.558
SOLD ONLY TO NEW YORK CITY
PUBLIC SCHOOLS.

13:45.592 --> 13:47.928
- THE PERP IS
FROM CATHERINE'S SCHOOL.

13:47.961 --> 13:49.529
- ISABELLE
WAS RIGHT ALL ALONG.

13:49.562 --> 13:51.598
- CUT KEVIN LOOSE.
HE'S BEEN THROUGH ENOUGH.

13:51.631 --> 13:54.834
- AND I THINK
WE SHOULD TELL CATHERINE.

13:58.171 --> 14:00.507
- BUT I WAS SO SURE
IT WAS KEVIN.

14:00.540 --> 14:01.909
- WELL,
IT'S LIKE YOU SAID,

14:01.942 --> 14:03.911
IT WAS DARK
AND YOU WERE TERRIFIED.

14:03.944 --> 14:06.213
- ISABELLE WILL NEVER
FORGIVE ME NOW.

14:06.246 --> 14:09.416
HOW DO I FIX THIS?

14:09.449 --> 14:12.319
- I DON'T THINK YOU CAN.
- WELL, I HAVE TO TRY.

14:12.352 --> 14:15.588
I FALSELY ACCUSED HER BROTHER
OF ATTACKING ME.

14:15.622 --> 14:18.325
- ARE YOU SURE
HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING?

14:18.358 --> 14:20.327
I HEARD HE HAD
A SEX CRIMES RECORD.

14:20.360 --> 14:22.896
- AND WE DON'T BELIEVE
HE WAS GUILTY OF THAT EITHER.

14:22.930 --> 14:24.898
- I LOST MY BEST FRIEND
FOR NOTHING.

14:24.932 --> 14:28.902
- HONEY,
YOU MADE A MISTAKE.

14:28.936 --> 14:31.204
BUT A MAN RAPED YOU.

14:31.238 --> 14:32.605
YOU KNOW HE WAS BLACK,

14:32.639 --> 14:35.642
AND HE'S STILL OUT THERE.

14:37.110 --> 14:38.178
- CATHERINE,
CAN YOU WALK ME THROUGH

14:38.211 --> 14:39.212
YOUR ATTACK ONE MORE TIME?

14:39.246 --> 14:41.614
- WHAT KIND OF PERSON
ARE YOU?

14:41.648 --> 14:42.482
YOU'RE GOING TO MAKE HER

14:42.515 --> 14:44.151
RELIVE THIS WHOLE THING
ALL OVER AGAIN?

14:44.184 --> 14:47.220
- SIR, I'M TRYING
TO FIND HER ATTACKER.

14:47.254 --> 14:48.956
NOW, CATHERINE,
WE HAVE NEW EVIDENCE

14:48.989 --> 14:51.024
ABOUT ANOTHER MAN.

14:51.058 --> 14:54.061
THAT CONNECTS HIM TO
THE SCHOOL THAT YOU TEACH AT.

14:55.695 --> 14:58.398
ISABELLE SAID
THAT YOU WERE THREATENED?

14:58.431 --> 15:00.533
- I DON'T WANNA BE
WRONG AGAIN.

15:00.567 --> 15:02.702
- WELL, WHY DON'T YOU
LET ME WORRY ABOUT THAT?

15:02.735 --> 15:06.373
TRUST ME, ANYTHING
YOU SAY CAN ONLY HELP.

15:13.646 --> 15:15.983
- THERE'S A GUY.
HE'S NEW.

15:16.016 --> 15:18.685
AHEM. HE BRINGS IN
FRESH VEGGIES EVERYDAY.

15:18.718 --> 15:20.687
IT'S A HUGE DEAL
IN A LOW-INCOME SCHOOL.

15:20.720 --> 15:22.355
- AND YOU HAD CONTACT
WITH HIM?

15:22.389 --> 15:23.623
- IN THE PARKING LOT.

15:23.656 --> 15:27.460
HE...STARED AT ME,
FILLED WITH RAGE,

15:27.494 --> 15:29.296
MUTTERING "EFFING BITCH"
UNDER HIS BREATH.

15:29.329 --> 15:30.630
- WHAT'S HIS NAME?

15:30.663 --> 15:34.001
- DWIGHT TALCOTT.
AND I'M CLEAN, DETECTIVES.

15:34.034 --> 15:36.436
LIVING THE QUIET LIFE.

15:36.469 --> 15:37.670
- WELL,
THAT'D BE A FIRST.

15:37.704 --> 15:41.041
WE LOOKED YOU UP.
A LIFETIME OF CHARGES.

15:41.074 --> 15:43.243
POSSESSION, BURGLARY,
YOU NAME IT.

15:43.276 --> 15:45.345
- AND I'M PLACING YOU
UNDER ARREST.

15:45.378 --> 15:47.180
- FOR WHAT?

15:47.214 --> 15:50.083
- BURGLARY, ASSAULT, AND
THE RAPE OF CATHERINE HARRISON.

15:50.117 --> 15:51.418
- I DON'T KNOW HER.

15:51.451 --> 15:55.255
- YOU ALWAYS CALL STRANGERS
"EFFIN' BITCHES?"

15:55.288 --> 15:57.190
- [gasps]
DWIGHT!

15:57.224 --> 15:58.258
WHAT'S GOING ON?

15:58.291 --> 15:59.726
- NOTHING, MA.

15:59.759 --> 16:01.628
LOOKS LIKE I WON'T
BE HOME FOR SUPPER, THOUGH.

16:01.661 --> 16:03.563
- YEAH, YOU CAN FORGET ABOUT
A HOME-COOKED MEAL

16:03.596 --> 16:05.698
ANYTIME IN YOUR FUTURE.
- THAT'S ALL RIGHT, SON.

16:05.732 --> 16:07.634
I'LL TAKE CARE OF YOU.

16:07.667 --> 16:09.602
- I TOLD YOU,

16:09.636 --> 16:11.271
I DON'T KNOW ANYBODY
NAMED CATHERINE HARRISON.

16:11.304 --> 16:12.672
- SURE YOU DO.

16:12.705 --> 16:15.142
YOU WERE CALLING HER NAMES IN
HER SCHOOL PARKING LOT.

16:15.175 --> 16:18.078
- THEN YOU STALKED HER,
THEN YOU RAPED HER.

16:18.111 --> 16:21.181
- LOOK, WE GOT EVIDENCE
PUTTING YOU IN HER ROOM.

16:21.214 --> 16:22.615
YOU WENT TO
AN AWFUL LOT OF TROUBLE

16:22.649 --> 16:25.152
CLIMBING UP
THAT FIRE ESCAPE,

16:25.185 --> 16:27.254
USING ALL YOUR BREAKING
AND ENTERING SKILLS

16:27.287 --> 16:29.022
TO GET IN THROUGH HER WINDOW.

16:29.056 --> 16:31.591
- GET OUT MY FACE.

16:31.624 --> 16:35.595
AND GET ME MY LAWYER.

16:35.628 --> 16:37.764
- HOW FAR DID YOU GET?
- NOWHERE.

16:37.797 --> 16:39.732
TALCOTT'S DOING LIFE
ON THE INSTALLMENT PLAN.

16:39.766 --> 16:41.101
THREE TO FIVE YEARS
AT A TIME.

16:41.134 --> 16:42.769
I MEAN, THERE'S
NO WAY HE'S CONFESSING.

16:42.802 --> 16:46.106
- LUCKY WE EVEN GOT
HIS NAME.

16:49.109 --> 16:51.044
- DWIGHT LOOKS CLEAN.

16:51.078 --> 16:52.245
- WHO ARE YOU?

16:52.279 --> 16:55.582
- JOE DEKKER,
DEPUTY D.A., LOS ANGELES.

16:55.615 --> 16:57.317
- WELL, SORRY,
WE FOUND HIM FIRST.

16:57.350 --> 17:00.387
- YOU'RE JURISDICTION'S
3,000 MILES HEADING WEST.

17:00.420 --> 17:02.589
- AND YOURS WAS PULLED OUT
FROM UNDERNEATH YOU.

17:02.622 --> 17:03.523
FROM WHAT I HEAR,

17:03.556 --> 17:06.226
YOU'RE VERY LUCKY
TO EVEN HAVE THIS JOB.

17:06.259 --> 17:08.295
- SMOOTH, YOU ALWAYS
OPEN WITH THE CHEAP SHOT?

17:08.328 --> 17:10.397
- WELL, IT WASN'T ME
LYING TO A JUDGE.

17:10.430 --> 17:12.099
NOW I WANT THE WARRANT

17:12.132 --> 17:14.467
AND EVERY LAST
BIT OF DISCOVERY YOU HAVE

17:14.501 --> 17:16.603
BY NO LATER THAN
CLOSE OF BUSINESS TODAY.

17:16.636 --> 17:18.638
- YOU'RE DEFENDING HIM?
- YES.

17:18.671 --> 17:20.540
- YOU KNOW, YOU NEED
TO BE LICENSED IN NEW YORK.

17:20.573 --> 17:22.575
- I AM.
DWIGHT IS FAMILY,

17:22.609 --> 17:24.144
AND HIS MOTHER LORNA
IS MY AUNT.

17:24.177 --> 17:25.678
- YOUR BOSS
KNOW YOU JUMPED SHIP?

17:25.712 --> 17:27.747
- UNLIKE YOU, I WENT THROUGH
THE PROPER CHANNELS.

17:27.780 --> 17:29.649
- NOW MY JOB HERE
IS TO ENSURE

17:29.682 --> 17:33.586
THAT THERE IS NO POLICE
OR PROSECUTORIAL MISCONDUCT.

17:33.620 --> 17:35.822
SO WE'LL BE SEEING
A LOT OF EACH OTHER.

17:35.855 --> 17:37.090
- GOODY, JUST WHAT WE
NEED AROUND HERE.

17:37.124 --> 17:38.191
ANOTHER ARROGANT PRICK.

17:38.225 --> 17:39.692
- YOU GOT THAT RIGHT,
DETECTIVE.

17:39.726 --> 17:42.729
CHECK MY CONVICTION RECORD,
AND YOU'LL SEE WHY.

17:55.408 --> 17:57.210
- THAT'S AN INTERESTING
TACTIC, COUNSELOR.

17:57.244 --> 17:59.146
I DON'T USUALLY SPEAK
WITH THE DEFENDANT'S MOTHER.

17:59.179 --> 18:00.613
- MS.TALCOTT
WAS WITH DWIGHT

18:00.647 --> 18:02.715
WHEN CATHERINE HARRISON
WAS ASSAULTED,

18:02.749 --> 18:04.717
PROVING HE COULDN'T
HAVE DONE IT.

18:04.751 --> 18:07.620
- RIGHT.
MOMMY ALIBIING HER SON.

18:07.654 --> 18:09.522
I NEVER
HEARD THAT ONE BEFORE.

18:09.556 --> 18:11.291
- MY SON IS NOT A RAPIST.

18:11.324 --> 18:12.825
- WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,
MS. TALCOTT,

18:12.859 --> 18:14.494
YOUR OPINION OF HIM
MAY BE BIASED.

18:14.527 --> 18:16.563
- I KNOW DWIGHT
BETTER THAN ANYBODY.

18:16.596 --> 18:19.232
MY SON IS AN ADDICT.

18:19.266 --> 18:20.767
A THIEF.

18:20.800 --> 18:23.470
HE'S STOLEN MONEY FROM ME,
AND MY FAMILY AND FRIENDS,

18:23.503 --> 18:25.572
TO BUY DRUGS.

18:25.605 --> 18:26.873
I'VE SPENT MY WHOLE LIFE

18:26.906 --> 18:29.342
WATCHING DWIGHT
THROW HIS AWAY.

18:29.376 --> 18:31.278
BUT HE'S NOT A RAPIST.

18:31.311 --> 18:32.645
- THAT YOU KNOW OF.

18:32.679 --> 18:34.247
- NO, THAT WE'RE SURE OF.

18:34.281 --> 18:36.216
HE'S A REPEAT
MIDDLE-AGED BURGLAR

18:36.249 --> 18:37.617
WHO'S NEVER BEEN ACCUSED

18:37.650 --> 18:40.153
OF EVEN ONE
SEXUALLY-MOTIVATED CRIME.

18:40.187 --> 18:42.755
NOW EXPLAIN THAT.
- THAT'S NOT MY JOB.

18:42.789 --> 18:45.758
I ONLY HAVE TO PROVE HE DID IT,
NOT HIS REASONS WHY.

18:45.792 --> 18:47.194
- GOOD LUCK,
SINCE HE WASN'T

18:47.227 --> 18:49.762
ANYWHERE NEAR
THE VICTIM'S BEDROOM.

18:49.796 --> 18:51.198
- WHAT'S THIS?

18:51.231 --> 18:53.466
- PROOF THAT DWIGHT
WAS WITH ME

18:53.500 --> 18:57.604
AT THE 177TH STREET
COMMUNITY CENTER AND GARDEN.

18:57.637 --> 19:01.241
- THEY HAVE
A SECURITY CAMERA.

19:01.274 --> 19:02.642
- HE WAS WITH YOU
THE WHOLE TIME?

19:02.675 --> 19:05.645
- HELPING HER ORGANIZE
COMMUNITY WATCH ROTATIONS.

19:05.678 --> 19:07.514
- SOMETHING I'VE BEEN DOING
SINCE MY DAYS

19:07.547 --> 19:10.817
WITH THE STUDENT NON-VIOLENT
COORDINATING COMMITTEE.

19:10.850 --> 19:13.820
WE GOT THERE AT 6:00,
LEFT AT MIDNIGHT.

19:13.853 --> 19:16.856
- CALL ME WHEN
YOU'RE DISMISSING THE CHARGES.

19:21.494 --> 19:23.630
- SO THIS IS SUPPOSED
TO CLEAR DWIGHT?

19:23.663 --> 19:25.665
- WELL, IF CATHERINE
FINGERED THE WRONG GUY AGAIN,

19:25.698 --> 19:27.467
HER CREDIBILITY IS SHOT.

19:27.500 --> 19:29.302
- HE HARASSED HER IN
THE PARKING LOT,

19:29.336 --> 19:30.503
HE TRANSFERRED
TRACE EVIDENCE

19:30.537 --> 19:31.704
FROM THE CAFETERIA
TO HER BEDROOM.

19:31.738 --> 19:33.773
- IF IT WAS HIS SHOE.

19:33.806 --> 19:35.508
- SO GET US A WARRANT.

19:35.542 --> 19:37.610
- NO, I WILL.
BUT DWIGHT'S NOT STUPID.

19:37.644 --> 19:39.679
YOU'D HAVE BETTER LUCK
FINDING THAT SHOE IN THE HUDSON.

19:39.712 --> 19:41.481
- I'VE SEEN
YOU WIN CASES ON LESS.

19:41.514 --> 19:43.983
- THAT WAS BEFORE
MY REPUTATION TOOK A NOSEDIVE.

19:44.016 --> 19:45.518
- MY MONEY'S ON YOU.

19:45.552 --> 19:47.787
- MM.
SO FAR, ALL I'M SEEING

19:47.820 --> 19:50.523
IS A ROCK SOLID ALIBI.
DWIGHT'S IN PLAIN VIEW,

19:50.557 --> 19:52.559
EXCEPT FOR A FEW MINUTES
WHEN HE HITS THE CAN.

19:52.592 --> 19:53.860
- FREEZE IT.

19:53.893 --> 19:55.928
HE JUST HEADED
OUT THE BACK DOOR.

19:55.962 --> 19:57.264
- HOW LONG
BEFORE HE COMES BACK?

19:57.297 --> 19:58.398
- HAVEN'T
GOTTEN THAT FAR YET.

19:58.431 --> 20:00.967
- OKAY,
SO HE LEAVES AT 8:20...

20:09.676 --> 20:11.511
DOESN'T GET BACK
UNTIL 9:13.

20:11.544 --> 20:13.480
- WELL, CATHERINE WAS
RAPED AT 8:45.

20:13.513 --> 20:15.348
THAT'S MORE THAN ENOUGH TIME
TO GO TO HER PLACE

20:15.382 --> 20:17.550
AND GET BACK.
- LOOK AT HIM, HE'S A MESS.

20:17.584 --> 20:20.787
- MAMA NEVER KNEW
HE SLIPPED OUT.

20:20.820 --> 20:23.923
- BUT A JURY WILL.

20:23.956 --> 20:26.693
YOUR CLIENT DIDN'T
COME BACK FOR 53 MINUTES.

20:26.726 --> 20:28.728
- PROVING ONLY
THAT YOU CAN TELL TIME.

20:28.761 --> 20:31.698
MY CLIENT COULD'VE BEEN ANYWHERE
OUT OF VIEW OF THAT CAMERA.

20:31.731 --> 20:34.301
- LIKE MY VICTIM'S BEDROOM.

20:34.334 --> 20:36.703
YOU KNOW,
IF YOU PLEAD GUILTY,

20:36.736 --> 20:38.338
I'LL DROP THE RAPE CHARGE.

20:38.371 --> 20:42.442
BURG ONE, 20 TO LIFE.
IT'S A ONE-TIME OFFER.

20:42.475 --> 20:43.843
- POKER IS NOT YOUR GAME.

20:43.876 --> 20:46.513
- WE'LL SEE
WHAT A JURY HAS TO SAY.

20:46.546 --> 20:47.580
- NOT GUILTY,

20:47.614 --> 20:49.749
IF ALL YOU HAVE TO PRESENT
IS PAPER-THIN FORENSICS

20:49.782 --> 20:52.552
AND A VICTIM WHO CAN'T
TELL ONE BLACK MAN FROM ANOTHER.

20:52.585 --> 20:54.921
ASSUMING, OF COURSE,
IF NEW YORK EVEN REQUIRES

20:54.954 --> 20:56.889
EVIDENCE
TO CONVICT SOMEONE.

20:56.923 --> 20:58.925
- L.A. IS THE LAND OF
JUSTICE, REALLY?

20:58.958 --> 21:01.694
- MS. NOVAK...

21:01.728 --> 21:03.496
- I DIDN'T RAPE THAT GIRL.

21:03.530 --> 21:05.965
- WHO DO YOU THINK
THEY'RE GONNA BELIEVE, DWIGHT?

21:05.998 --> 21:07.467
AN INNOCENT SCHOOL TEACHER

21:07.500 --> 21:08.868
OR A CRACKED-OUT
MULTIPLE FELON?

21:11.804 --> 21:14.073
SEE YOU IN COURT.
- LOOKING FORWARD TO IT,

21:14.106 --> 21:17.310
SINCE YOU AND JUDGE PETROVSKY
ARE SO WELL-ACQUAINTED.

21:30.557 --> 21:31.824
- MS. HARRISON...

21:31.858 --> 21:33.960
CAN YOU PLEASE
TELL THE MEMBERS OF THE JURY

21:33.993 --> 21:35.962
WHAT HAPPENED
AFTER YOU WENT TO SLEEP

21:35.995 --> 21:37.664
ON THE NIGHT IN QUESTION?

21:37.697 --> 21:38.965
- I WOKE UP

21:38.998 --> 21:42.935
WHEN I FELT SOMEONE
ON TOP OF ME.

21:42.969 --> 21:45.538
I THOUGHT BELLE
WAS PLAYING A JOKE.

21:45.572 --> 21:49.709
SHE ALWAYS MAKES FUN OF ME
BECAUSE I GO TO BED EARLY.

21:49.742 --> 21:53.846
[door opening]

21:53.880 --> 21:55.648
- AT WHAT POINT DID YOU
REALIZE

21:55.682 --> 21:57.484
THAT IT WASN'T A PRANK?

21:57.517 --> 22:02.389
WHEN MY RAPIST RIPPED UP
MY NIGHTGOWN AND MY UNDERWEAR.

22:02.422 --> 22:04.090
- AND DO YOU SEE THAT MAN
IN THE COURTROOM TODAY?

22:04.123 --> 22:05.892
- YES.

22:05.925 --> 22:07.126
OVER THERE.

22:07.159 --> 22:08.595
- WHAT HAPPENED NEXT?

22:08.628 --> 22:10.563
- I THOUGHT
HE WAS GONNA KILL ME.

22:10.597 --> 22:14.934
HE BANGED THE WALL
BEHIND MY HEAD A FEW TIMES,

22:14.967 --> 22:17.770
AND UNBUCKLED HIS PANTS.

22:17.804 --> 22:21.007
I WAS CRYING, SO...

22:21.040 --> 22:24.811
HE PUT HIS HAND
OVER MY MOUTH.

22:24.844 --> 22:27.013
AND THEN HE...

22:27.046 --> 22:29.549
HE...
- HE RAPED YOU?

22:29.582 --> 22:31.784
- OBJECTION, LEADING.
- SUSTAINED.

22:31.818 --> 22:34.487
- WHAT HAPPENED NEXT,
CATHERINE?

