THEN A CAR PULLS UP.

34:10.582 --> 34:14.620
PULLS US BOTH INSIDE.

34:14.653 --> 34:17.389
SIX YEARS OLD...

34:17.423 --> 34:20.426
I GOT A GUN TO MY HEAD.

34:23.895 --> 34:27.466
THEY MAKE ME...WATCH...

34:30.636 --> 34:34.206
WHILE THEY...

34:34.240 --> 34:38.344
RAPED HER.

34:38.377 --> 34:40.646
SOMETIMES TWO AT ONCE.

34:40.679 --> 34:42.714
- AND AFTER ALL THIS TIME,

34:42.748 --> 34:44.883
YOU DECIDED TO FIND GRANT.

34:44.916 --> 34:47.619
WHY?

34:47.653 --> 34:49.755
- I STARTED
HAVING THESE NIGHTMARES,

34:49.788 --> 34:51.323
SEEING IT
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

34:51.357 --> 34:54.726
AND I KNEW THE ONLY WAY
I WAS GONNA STOP THE PAIN

34:54.760 --> 34:57.529
WAS TO FIND HER RAPIST.

34:57.563 --> 34:59.665
SO...

34:59.698 --> 35:02.901
I HIRED
A PRIVATE DETECTIVE.

35:02.934 --> 35:06.405
IT TURNED OUT GRANT
WAS THE ONLY ONE STILL ALIVE.

35:06.438 --> 35:09.408
I GOT HIS ADDRESS
FROM THE FILES.

35:09.441 --> 35:11.343
- BUT WHY RAPE CATHERINE?

35:11.377 --> 35:14.380
- 'CAUSE I WANTED GRANT
TO KNOW WHAT IT FELT LIKE.

35:15.514 --> 35:18.517
KNOWING HE COULDN'T
PROTECT SOMEBODY HE LOVED.

35:29.261 --> 35:33.665
WHY DON'T YOU
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED...

35:33.699 --> 35:37.303
THE NIGHT YOU BROKE
INTO CATHERINE'S BEDROOM.

35:37.336 --> 35:39.305
- I MADE SURE SHE WAS ASLEEP,

35:39.338 --> 35:41.807
THEN I BROKE IN FROM
THE FIRE ESCAPE, WEARING GLOVES.

35:41.840 --> 35:43.675
- WHAT DID YOU INTEND TO DO

35:43.709 --> 35:45.877
ONCE YOU GOT INSIDE
THE VICTIM'S BEDROOM?

35:45.911 --> 35:46.878
- TEACH HER OLD MAN
A LESSON.

35:46.912 --> 35:49.815
I CLIMBED ON THE BED,
AND CATHERINE WOKE UP.

35:49.848 --> 35:53.252
I RIPPED HER CLOTHES.

35:55.587 --> 35:58.357
THEN, UM...
[clears throat]

35:58.390 --> 36:00.326
- INSTRUCT YOUR CLIENT

36:00.359 --> 36:02.894
WE NEED A FULL STATEMENT
FOR THE RECORD.

36:02.928 --> 36:05.931
- YOU'RE UNDER OATH,
DWIGHT.

36:09.568 --> 36:12.271
- TELL THE TRUTH, SON.

36:19.978 --> 36:21.947
- I DID NOT RAPE
CATHERINE HARRISON.

36:21.980 --> 36:26.352
- I THOUGHT THE DEFENDANT
AGREED TO PLEAD GUILTY?

36:26.385 --> 36:28.620
- DID YOU RAPE
CATHERINE HARRISON?

36:28.654 --> 36:30.889
- NO.

36:30.922 --> 36:32.023
I KEPT SEEING GRANT
AND HIS FRIENDS

36:32.057 --> 36:34.960
HOLDING MY MOTHER'S LEGS WIDE
WHILE THEY RAPED HER.

36:34.993 --> 36:36.995
THEY LAUGHED
WHILE THEY BEAT HER,

36:37.028 --> 36:39.731
AND SHE SCREAMED.

36:39.765 --> 36:42.734
I COULDN'T BRING MYSELF
TO DO THAT.

36:42.768 --> 36:44.336
IT'S NOT WHO I AM.

36:46.738 --> 36:49.775
- PERJURY VOIDS YOUR DEAL.
- I'M AWARE OF THAT.

36:49.808 --> 36:51.677
- DID YOU HAVE
FORCIBLE INTERCOURSE

36:51.710 --> 36:53.945
WITH THE VICTIM OR NOT?

36:53.979 --> 36:55.914
- NO, YOUR HONOR.

36:55.947 --> 36:58.884
SO GIVE ME MY SENTENCE
FOR BREAKING AND ENTERING.

36:58.917 --> 37:00.819
- BOTH OF YOU, BENCH,
NOW.

37:06.057 --> 37:08.260
- LOOKS TO ME LIKE
YOU'RE TRYING TO RAILROAD

37:08.294 --> 37:10.296
ANOTHER DEFENDANT
INTO PRISON, MS. NOVAK.

37:10.329 --> 37:11.830
- YOUR HONOR,
BOTH DWIGHT TALCOTT

37:11.863 --> 37:13.732
AND HIS ATTORNEY
AGREED TO THE DEAL.

37:13.765 --> 37:15.033
- WHY WON'T
HE CONFESS TO RAPE?

37:15.066 --> 37:17.035
- MAYBE SOMEONE
CHANGED HIS MIND FOR HIM.

37:17.068 --> 37:18.770
- OR MAYBE
HE JUST DIDN'T DO IT.

37:18.804 --> 37:20.339
- THE VICTIM SAID HE DID.

37:20.372 --> 37:23.409
- YOUR HONOR, MY CLIENT'S
ALREADY FACING LIFE

37:23.442 --> 37:25.677
FOR BURGLARY AND ASSAULT.

37:25.711 --> 37:28.480
I MEAN, WHY NOT CONFESS
TO RAPING CATHERINE

37:28.514 --> 37:29.948
UNLESS HE'S NOT GUILTY.

37:29.981 --> 37:32.351
- A VERY GOOD QUESTION.

37:32.384 --> 37:33.985
I SUGGEST YOU FIND OUT

37:34.019 --> 37:36.722
BEFORE YOU WASTE
ANYMORE OF MY TIME.

37:46.665 --> 37:47.966
- IS IT TRUE?

37:47.999 --> 37:51.970
DID MY GRANDFATHER
RAPE DWIGHT TALCOTT'S MOTHER?

37:52.003 --> 37:54.473
- ALONG WITH
TWO OF HIS KLAN BUDDIES.

37:54.506 --> 37:56.908
- I HAD NO IDEA.

37:56.942 --> 37:59.010
HE LIED TO ME.

38:00.879 --> 38:03.882
- WHO LIED?

38:07.386 --> 38:10.922
- I-I CAN'T DO THIS,
I'M SORRY.

38:10.956 --> 38:13.392
- DID DWIGHT TALCOTT
RAPE YOU, CATHERINE?

38:13.425 --> 38:15.927
- I ALREADY TOLD YOU.

38:15.961 --> 38:17.963
- WELL, TELL US AGAIN.

38:17.996 --> 38:19.631
DID DWIGHT TALCOTT
RAPE YOU?

38:19.665 --> 38:21.700
- OR DID
YOUR GRANDFATHER TELL YOU

38:21.733 --> 38:24.636
TO SAY THAT HE DID?

38:24.670 --> 38:26.805
- YOU DON'T
KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE.

38:26.838 --> 38:29.074
I...LOVE PAPA.

38:29.107 --> 38:31.910
HE RAISED ME.

38:31.943 --> 38:34.946
- WHAT DID
GRANT TELL YOU TO DO?

38:36.548 --> 38:38.550
- HE TOLD ME...

38:38.584 --> 38:41.720
YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE ME
IF I DIDN'T SAY IT WAS RAPE.

38:41.753 --> 38:44.823
HE SAID BLACK MEN RAPE.

38:44.856 --> 38:48.794
HE'S BEEN TELLING ME THAT
MY ENTIRE LIFE.

38:48.827 --> 38:51.963
BUT I AM NOT LIKE HIM.

38:51.997 --> 38:53.031
I SWEAR THAT--

38:53.064 --> 38:55.934
I WORK AT THAT SCHOOL,

38:55.967 --> 38:57.035
I MOVED
TO WASHINGTON HEIGHTS.

38:57.068 --> 38:58.970
- TO PROVE TO YOURSELF
THAT YOU WERE NOT LIKE HIM.

38:59.004 --> 39:00.872
- YOU LIED UNDER OATH.

39:00.906 --> 39:04.743
OKAY, TO ME, TO THE JUDGE,
TO THE JURY.

39:09.948 --> 39:11.483
DO IT.

39:11.517 --> 39:13.485
- FACE THAT WAY, PUT
YOUR HANDS BEHIND YOUR BACK.

39:13.519 --> 39:16.822
- I DIDN'T MEAN FOR THIS
TO HAPPEN.

39:16.855 --> 39:18.690
[crying]
I...

39:18.724 --> 39:20.626
PAPA SAID I WAS CONFUSED.

39:20.659 --> 39:22.160
HE SAID TO SAY I WAS RAPED

39:22.193 --> 39:24.996
OR NO ONE WOULD BELIEVE
DWIGHT ATTACKED ME.

39:25.030 --> 39:26.732
- DEKKER...

39:26.765 --> 39:27.799
YEAH.

39:27.833 --> 39:29.668
- WAIT.

39:29.701 --> 39:30.869
WHAT'S GOING ON?

39:30.902 --> 39:32.070
- YOUR GRANDDAUGHTER'S
GOING TO JAIL.

39:32.103 --> 39:33.705
- WHAT THE HELL FOR?

39:33.739 --> 39:35.974
- PERJURY.
YOU GAVE HER BAD ADVICE.

39:36.007 --> 39:37.643
HER ARRAIGNMENT'S TOMORROW,
YOU CAN SEE HER THEN.

39:37.676 --> 39:39.945
- DON'T WORRY, BABY.
I'LL GET THE BAIL TO GIVE--

39:39.978 --> 39:42.380
- ALL MY LIFE YOU HAVE
TAUGHT ME TO HATE.

39:44.816 --> 39:46.885
I HATE WHAT YOU SAY.

39:46.918 --> 39:49.421
I HATE WHAT YOU THINK.

39:49.455 --> 39:53.759
I HATE YOU.

39:53.792 --> 39:55.861
GO TO HELL.

40:09.975 --> 40:12.978
- MS. HARRISON...

40:14.913 --> 40:17.883
I'M SORRY.

40:17.916 --> 40:19.818
I'M REALLY SORRY.

40:19.851 --> 40:22.854
- I AM TOO.

40:29.861 --> 40:31.897
- 20 TO LIFE,
STILL ON THE TABLE.

40:31.930 --> 40:34.933
- MAKE IT 15,
AND YOU'VE GOT A DEAL.

